                    </svg>
                    <span class="text-sm text-gray-500">Usually delivered within <b>4-6 days</b></span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex gap-3 items-center">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="green" height="20" width="20" viewBox="0 0 640 512"><!--!Font Awesome Free 6.5.1 by @fontawesome - https://fontawesome.com License - https://fontawesome.com/license/free Copyright 2023 Fonticons, Inc.-->
                        <path d="M96 96V320c0 35.3 28.7 64 64 64H576c35.3 0 64-28.7 64-64V96c0-35.3-28.7-64-64-64H160c-35.3 0-64 28.7-64 64zm64 160c35.3 0 64 28.7 64 64H160V256zM224 96c0 35.3-28.7 64-64 64V96h64zM576 256v64H512c0-35.3 28.7-64 64-64zM512 96h64v64c-35.3 0-64-28.7-64-64zM288 208a80 80 0 1 1 160 0 80 80 0 1 1 -160 0zM48 120c0-13.3-10.7-24-24-24S0 106.7 0 120V360c0 66.3 53.7 120 120 120H520c13.3 0 24-10.7 24-24s-10.7-24-24-24H120c-39.8 0-72-32.2-72-72V120z"/>
                    </svg>
                    <span class="text-sm text-gray-500">Cash On Delivery <b>available</b></span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex gap-3 items-center">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="green" height="20" width="20" viewBox="0 0 512 512"><!--!Font Awesome Free 6.5.1 by @fontawesome - https://fontawesome.com License - https://fontawesome.com/license/free Copyright 2023 Fonticons, Inc.-->
